                        "id": "7-rv5361r",
                        "content": "[ ] Setup\nSetting, action, dialogue.\nObjective, conflict, change in value, infodump.\nPrecise outline if needed, what needs to happen.\n\nWrite a paragraph about the world where the story takes place.\n\nDescribe a character in a situation.",
