                    {
                        "id": "10-8p836m6",
                        "content": "[ ] Challenge/problem\n\nDescribe the event that disrupts the normal course of events and begins the story. What can go wrong? What problem is character facing? What goal does he have? Who is the antagonist?",
                        "children": []
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "8-8p636lq",
                        "content": "[ ] Escalate\nProgress/Setbacks, 3 attempts, \nrandom encounters, plan stages\n\nHow can things escalate? How does the character pursue his goal, what obstacles/challenes does he need to overcome? How can things spiral out of control, raising the stakes, requiring bigger and bigger risks, leading to the showdown between the hero and antagonist?",
                        "children": []
                    },
                    {
                        "id": "9-nl736ou",
                        "content": "[ ] Resolve\nHow does it end? Does the character win? How? Why?\nDid the world go back to normal? What changed?\n(change in value)",
